code: private static Map<String, String> parseEnvVariables(Map<String, String> args) {     if (args == null || args.isEmpty()) {         return Collections.emptyMap().     }     Map<String, String> result = new LinkedHashMap<>().     for (Map.Entry<String, String> e : args.entrySet()) {         if (e.getKey() != null) {             result.put(e.getKey(), getValue(e.getValue())).         }     }     return result. }
private static String getValue(String value) {     return (value != null) ? value : "". }

public String[] asArray() {     List<String> args = new ArrayList<>(this.variables.size()).     for (Map.Entry<String, String> arg : this.variables.entrySet()) {         args.add(arg.getKey() + "=" + arg.getValue()).     }     return args.toArray(new String[0]). }
